imdb.plot outline: Paranormal Awakening is a YouTube series that follows the group New River Paranormal Society as they investigate areas claiming to be haunted. The group investigates these locations and reveals the evidence to the clients. Some locations are so bad that an exorcism or blessing of the location is needed to eliminate these entities from our realm.
imdb.title: Paranormal Awakening
plot: _Paranormal Awakening_ (qv) is a YouTube series that follows the group New River Paranormal Society as they investigate areas claiming to be haunted. The group investigates these locations and reveals the evidence to the clients. Some locations are so bad that an exorcism or blessing of the location is needed to eliminate these entities from our realm.::Michael Breen
